data.description: Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom gem offers a unique opportunity to create your dream home. With a generous 1560 sq ft of space, this residence provides a canvas for your imagination. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the cozy ambiance of the living room, complete with a charming fireplace that invites warm gatherings on chilly evenings. The primary bedroom, strategically located upstairs, provides a retreat-like feel while the other two bedrooms are on the main floor. Venture outside to discover your own private oasis. A pond adorns the backyard, creating a serene atmosphere. The roof and HVAC system and windows have been updated/replaced in the past 5 years. Bamboo flooring on the main floor, and carpeted bedrooms. The bonus room off the kitchen can be used for dining or as an at-home office space. To the left of the driveway, there is RV parking availability. This property is being sold "as-is" allowing the freedom to shape it according to your vision.
